---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About StableHeat — Electric Radiant Heating">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="kicker">About</span>
      <h1>Electric radiant heat, engineered to disappear.</h1>
      <p>StableHeat (formerly STEP Heat) has been designing self-regulating radiant heating systems for more than three decades — for the homes, buildings, driveways, and vessels where comfort can't be an afterthought.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-card">
          <span class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-temperature-half" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
          <h3>Self-regulating by design</h3>
          <p>Every StableHeat element adapts locally to what's happening above it. Cold zones draw more; warm zones back off. No hot spots, no worries about what's on top of the floor.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-card">
          <span class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
          <h3>Low-voltage safety</h3>
          <p>Our systems run at safe low voltages, with factory-sealed elements that tolerate the moisture and temperature swings of bathrooms, marine holds, and outdoor slabs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-card">
          <span class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-leaf" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
          <h3>Cleaner, quieter comfort</h3>
          <p>No ductwork means no circulating dust, no blower noise, and no forced-air dryness. You feel warmth instead of hearing it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-card">
          <span class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-house" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
          <h3>Built for how you live</h3>
          <p>From custom homes to hotel lobbies, yacht decks to RV floors, StableHeat is engineered to fit projects of every scale — residential, commercial, and industrial.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="about-body">
    <h2>Our applications</h2>
    <p><strong>Warmfloor</strong> — Under-tile, under-hardwood, and under-vinyl radiant for homes, offices, healthcare spaces, and hospitality.</p>
    <p><strong>Snowmelt</strong> — Embedded heating elements for driveways, walkways, ADA ramps, and commercial aprons. Clears precipitation automatically and safely.</p>
    <p><strong>Marine</strong> — Low-voltage, moisture-safe radiant built for below-deck living, from custom yachts to liveaboards and expedition hulls.</p>
    <p><strong>Industrial / OEM</strong> — Heat trace and custom heating elements for process equipment, tanks, and OEM integrations.</p>

    <h2>Based in St. Louis. Shipping everywhere.</h2>
    <p>Our team of engineers, designers, and installers is headquartered in St. Louis, Missouri, with a distributor and installer network across North America. Whether you're designing a single bathroom or specifying heat for a hundred-unit multifamily build, we'd love to help.</p>
    <p>Call us at <a href="tel:+13142025540">314.202.5540</a>, email <a href="mailto:sales@stableheat.com">sales@stableheat.com</a>, or visit <a href="https://stepheat.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">stableheat.com</a> for product information, specs, and installation resources.</p>
  </div>

  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="container">
      <div>
        <h2>Start your project.</h2>
        <p>We'll help you scope, spec, and source the right StableHeat system for your application.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex; gap:14px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://stepheat.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit stableheat.com →</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/" style="color:#fff; border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">Read the blog</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
